Gloria Winters https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gloria_Winters 0 Gloria Winters (November 28, 1931, in Los Angeles, California – August 14, 2010, in Vista, San Diego County, California) was an actress most remembered for having portrayed the well-mannered niece, Penny King, in the 1950s – 1960s American television series Sky King.
